ActCanadian Wheat Board Act
SubjectBARLEY - 2010-2011 UNSOLD STOCK ** Transfer to 2011 Pool **
PrecisOrder authorizing THE CANADIAN WHEAT BOARD to transfer unsold BARLEY stocks from the preceding pool that began on August 1, 2010, and ended on January 31, 2011, to the current pool period that began on February 1, 2011, and will end on July 31, 2011.
